data.text:
Are you ready to get the job?

From being unemployed & searching, to recently employed & adjusting, to gainfully employed & succeeding;

We are here every step of the way!

We empower people to achieve economic independence and self-sufficiency through career development, training, a network of support, and professional image services, resulting in gainful employment.

Our Programs & Services

Employment Skills

We can help you with anything career related, from resume writing to interview preparation, and anything in between.

Career Consulting

Get matched with one of our coaches to get guidance & receive support in order to gain lifelong career success.

Veteran Support

Our Vets for Success Program aims to help veterans and spouses transition into the civilian workforce. We provide a wide rage of classes and one-on-one services.

Professional Attire

We will put together professional attire to get you feeling confident the day of your interview.

Training Workshops

Join our experts in their workshops and classes to acquire the skills and confidence necessary to reach your career goals.

S.T.A.R.T Now

Smart Teens Are Responsible for Tomorrow Now, teaches teens the importance of career readiness and business etiquette.

Thirty years of empowering job-ready individuals and creating systemic change in their lives, their families and our community. Thank you to the individuals, foundations and corporations which allow us to serve the Miami-Dade community.

Upcoming events.

We like to keep our clients, volunteers and partners involved and updated with our busy schedule. Find out important dates; including events, workshops and when our office is closed.
